{
  "stem": "3040.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "While the others were out-- went out to work every day, I was hiding in-- in-- in that-- someplace in-- in the cellar.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And then we found somebody who was able to furnish us with-- with false identity cards.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we bought these identity cards for myself and for my wife.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I knew that it's dangerous to stay in this ghetto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I knew this is not going to last, because there's no reason they would leave 250 people and isolated there, that eventually they will ship us.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "It's a-- it was a matter of time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "After we got these identity cards, we left the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We went to the railroad station.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We are going to go to Cracow.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "In Cracow there was the ghetto already, and I had two brothers there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So I thought, maybe I'll be able to get into the ghetto in Cracow.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "It's a large ghetto, and I have my brothers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I-- I feel a little more secure.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "While we were waiting for the train there was an inspection of identity cards, and you can imagine our heart beating.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "How-- what-- how they will accept our brand-new identity cards?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they passed inspection.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Did you have a different name?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course, a different name.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Jan [?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Migawa ?] was my name.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we passed inspection, and we safely arrived in Cracow-- actually not in Cracow.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a suburb of Cracow, because the train didn't go all the way to Cracow.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And at this time, there was a curfew.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "After 9 o'clock, you shouldn't be seen in the street.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we couldn't leave the train station and go to the ghetto because it was after 9 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
